WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:02.300
<i>Previously on "Heartland:"</i>

00:02.401 --> 00:04.235
Yeah, I gotta see a woman
about a horse.

00:04.302 --> 00:05.869
In Golden B.C.?

00:05.936 --> 00:07.637
Isn't that like 300 kilometres
from here?

00:07.703 --> 00:08.903
Not as the crow flies.

00:08.971 --> 00:10.437
You haven't lost assistant
yet.

00:10.503 --> 00:11.503
Yeah, but Amy...

00:11.571 --> 00:13.004
I know,
it's our last day.

00:13.070 --> 00:14.670
No, whatever!
I...

00:14.738 --> 00:16.672
It just would've been nice
to spend some time together.

00:16.738 --> 00:18.606
<i>Okay, you know what?</i>
<i>I don't care!</i>

00:18.672 --> 00:20.006
<i>Yeah, do what you want.</i>

00:23.074 --> 00:24.774
Really?

00:24.841 --> 00:26.007
<i>Well, it looks like you're</i>
<i>gonna be a good father one day.</i>

00:26.074 --> 00:28.175
That's definitely
part of the plan.

00:28.242 --> 00:29.476
What plan?

00:29.541 --> 00:30.408
Life plan.

00:30.476 --> 00:31.709
What do you think?

00:31.775 --> 00:32.942
<i>Ty:</i>
<i>Amy would love this!</i>

00:33.009 --> 00:34.510
That's why
I'm giving to you.

00:34.577 --> 00:35.510
See you, Jane.

00:35.578 --> 00:37.345
(Plane buzzes overhead)

00:37.411 --> 00:38.877
Where are they?
Are they all right?

00:38.945 --> 00:42.046
That's the thing,
we don't know.

00:42.113 --> 00:44.481
<i>We'll let you know</i>
<i>the minute we get any news.</i>

00:46.000 --> 00:52.074
